description: This is a market group over what Donald J. Trump will say during his rally in Prescott Valley, Arizona scheduled for October 13, 2024.

markets.description:
Donald Trump has scheduled a rally on October 13 in Prescott Valley, Arizona (see: https://event.donaldjtrump.com/events/president-donald-j-trump-to-hold-a-rally-in-prescott-arizona).

The resolution source will be the video of the event.
